## Configuration

Agent behavior is configured in `.tapps-agents/config.yaml`:

```yaml
agents:
  reviewer:
    quality_threshold: 70  # Minimum overall score
    security_threshold: 7.0
    maintainability_threshold: 7.0
  
  implementer:
    require_review: true
    auto_approve_threshold: 80.0
    backup_files: true
  
  tester:
    coverage_threshold: 80.0
    generate_integration_tests: true
```

